embodied ghost, deep inside the mathematical community's understanding of counting.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aPHILOSOPHY / Metaphysics.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362213540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503622135423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503622135/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles